### **4. 34_LivePlotBuilder**  
**Description:**  
A real-time chart renderer that updates graphs based on data stream input.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LivePlotBuilder - Real-Time Data Charting

LivePlotBuilder creates animated line charts using live data, useful for IoT, dashboards, and demos.

## Features
- Dynamic update loop  
- Matplotlib backend  
- Adjustable input simulation  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_LivePlotBuilder.git
cd 34_LivePlotBuilder
python visualize.py
